title Airavat Unified Infra and Tool Architecture - Tiers 1 to 10

direction right

Runtime Plane [icon: server, color: teal] {
  FastAPI Control Surface [icon: terminal, label: "src/api/main.py + portal_routes.py"]
  Worker Fleet [icon: users, label: "classifier worker\nfeature worker\ncredit scoring worker\nintervention agent"]
}

Data Plane [icon: database, color: gray] {
  Redis Streams [icon: layers, label: "raw_ingestion, typed_events, behavioural_features\ncredit_requests, reasoning_events, vigilance_events, notifications"]
  Redis PubSub [icon: radio, label: "twin_updated, simulation_completed\nupdates:{task_id}, credit_events"]
  Redis Keyspaces [icon: hard-drive, label: "twin, features, score, credit, sim, tier5, tier8, tier9, audit"]
  Parquet Lake [icon: archive, label: "data/raw + data/features partitions"]
}

Tool and Algorithm Plane [icon: cpu, color: purple] {
  Tier1 Synth [icon: package, label: "Faker + NumPy + optional SDV + Polars"]
  Tier2 Semantics [icon: zap, label: "Regex rules + MiniLM + cosine similarity"]
  Tier3 Features [icon: bar-chart-2, label: "Polars windows + EMA + KNNImputer + IsolationForest"]
  Tier4 Twin [icon: user, label: "Pydantic state + deterministic 32-d DNA projection"]
  Tier5 Reasoning [icon: message-square, label: "z-test/LCI contradiction + OpenRouter CoT + fallback"]
  Tier6 Simulation [icon: shuffle, label: "Monte Carlo + Markov regime + GARCH + copula shocks"]
  Tier7 Credit [icon: trending-up, label: "Dual XGBoost + SHAP + APScheduler recalibration"]
  Tier8 Intervention [icon: bell, label: "trigger relevance + negotiation simulator + audit zsets"]
  Tier9 Vigilance [icon: shield, label: "NetworkX SCC/cycles/PageRank + Bayesian scam + JS drift"]
  Tier10 Compliance [icon: check-square, label: "cross-tier bundle collector + JSON/PDF export + live what-if"]
}

Tier Dependencies [icon: git-branch, color: orange] {
  Tier1To2 [icon: arrow-right, label: "canonical events"]
  Tier2To3 [icon: arrow-right, label: "typed events"]
  Tier3ToCore [icon: arrow-right, label: "features -> twin/sim/score/vigilance"]
  TwinToReasoningIntervention [icon: arrow-right, label: "twin state -> tier5/tier8"]
  AllToTier10 [icon: arrow-right, label: "evidence aggregation"]
}

FastAPI Control Surface --> Worker Fleet: starts and coordinates runtime services
Worker Fleet --> Redis Streams: consume and publish stream workloads
Worker Fleet --> Redis PubSub: publish event notifications
Worker Fleet --> Redis Keyspaces: persist operational states
Tier1 Synth --> Parquet Lake: write raw partitions
Tier3 Features --> Parquet Lake: write feature partitions
Parquet Lake --> Tier7 Credit: model training input

Tier1 Synth --> Tier1To2: produce canonical events
Tier1To2 --> Tier2 Semantics: semantic enrichment stage
Tier2 Semantics --> Tier2To3: publish typed events
Tier2To3 --> Tier3 Features: feature computation stage
Tier3 Features --> Tier3ToCore: provide behavioural vectors
Tier3ToCore --> Tier4 Twin: update digital twin
Tier3ToCore --> Tier6 Simulation: build simulation snapshots
Tier3ToCore --> Tier7 Credit: score user credit
Tier3ToCore --> Tier9 Vigilance: run vigilance detectors
Tier4 Twin --> TwinToReasoningIntervention: publish twin context
TwinToReasoningIntervention --> Tier5 Reasoning: generate narratives and flags
TwinToReasoningIntervention --> Tier8 Intervention: trigger interventions
Tier4 Twin --> AllToTier10: twin evidence
Tier5 Reasoning --> AllToTier10: reasoning evidence
Tier6 Simulation --> AllToTier10: simulation evidence
Tier7 Credit --> AllToTier10: credit evidence
Tier8 Intervention --> AllToTier10: intervention and audit evidence
Tier9 Vigilance --> AllToTier10: vigilance evidence
AllToTier10 --> Tier10 Compliance: assemble compliance outputs
